episodes.title: Cult of Weinstein
episodes.description:
Join us on our premiere episode of Unshut Cases where we unpack the Harvey Weinstein accusations and trials and see how they relate to human trafficking, the #MeeToo moment’s impact on workplace culture, and cult mentality. 
Our guest is employment lawyer and “cult assassin” Carol Merchasin  of McAllister Olivarius who gives her expert insight on this case and shares her stories of taking down cults and investigating spiritual communities.
